 KeyPad buttons' functions assignment

 1. umugati     200 Rwf
 2. Icyayi      200 Rwf
 3. umureti     1500 Rwf
 4. special     2000 Rwf
 5. ibishyimo   500 Rwf
 6. ifiriti     1000 Rwf
 7. inyama      1500 Rwf
 8. umuceri     500 Rwf
 9. isosi       200 Rwf
 D. cancel the request
 C. confirm / send

 KeyPad connection schema

 KeyPad ====> Arduino
    R1  ====> A0  
    R2  ====> A1
    R3  ====> A2
    R4  ====> A3
    C1  ====> A4
    C2  ====> A5
    C3  ====> 02
    C4  ====> 03

Lcd Dis ====> Arduino
    RS  ====> 11  
    E   ====> 08
    D4  ====> 04
    D5  ====> 05
    D6  ====> 06
    D7  ====> 07

Please read everything carefully!!